Dear <%= @membership.user.first_name %>,

This notice is to inform you that you have been assigned a membership in <%= @membership.description %>, for a term starting at <%= @membership.starts_at.to_s :rfc822 %> and ending at <%= @membership.ends_at.to_s :rfc822 %>.

<% if @membership.position.authority.join_notice -%>
<%= @membership.position.authority.join_notice %>

<% end -%>
<% if @membership.position.join_notice -%>
<%= @membership.position.join_notice %>

<% end -%>
<% if @membership.position.enrollments.length > 0 -%>
Concurrent with your appointment to this position, you hold the following committee enrollment:
<% @membership.position.enrollments.each do |enrollment| -%>
<%= enrollment.title %> of <%= enrollment.committee %> with <%= pluralize enrollment.votes, 'vote' %>
<% if enrollment.committee.join_message -%>
<%= enrollment.committee.join_message %>
<% end -%>

<% end -%>
<% end -%>

